Package project.star_wars_universe.cli.commands

Interface Command

All Known Implementing Classes:
AddPlanet, Close, CreateJedi, DemoteJedi, Exit, GetMostUsedSaberColor, GetMostUsedSaberColor.GetMostUsedSaberColorByGrandMasterOnPlanet, GetMostUsedSaberColor.GetMostUsedSaberColorOfRankOnPlanet, GetStrongestJedi, GetYoungestJedi, Help, Open, Print, PrintAllJedi, PrintAllPlanets, PrintCombinedPlanetsInfo, PromoteJedi, RemoveJedi, Save, SaveAs
public interface Command
Describes the contract for implementing a CLI command. The concrete classes must encapsulate the logic related to executing a certain CLI command - arguments, dependencies and the delegation of work to other classes of the application.

    • execute

      void execute(List<String> input) throws CommandExecutionException
      Executes a desired behaviour. This behaviour can either be delegated to other classes of the application or implemented inside the execute method itself.
      Parameters:
      input - the user input.
      Throws:
      CommandExecutionException - if the command execution fails.
